{"tid":1223787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警射催淚彈擊中急救站 陳沛然轟警妄顧醫護傷者安危","createTime":"2019-06-14T19:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T21:02:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"48d664913c56453d725d703031966f05a401490d","tid":1223787,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:40:04.000Z","msg":"數以萬計示威者前日早上自發佔領金鐘主幹道，舉起雨傘並戴上口罩抵擋警方的胡椒噴霧與警棍，立法會會議被迫押後。警方其後將示威定性為暴亂，出動布袋彈、橡膠彈、催淚彈對付手無寸鐵的示威者，立法會醫學界議員陳沛然表示指，早前收到醫護人員投訴，稱前日大規模示威活動時，警方發射催淚彈擊中在金鐘龍和道和添美道交界廻旋處的急救站，導致在場的醫護人員感到不適，批評警方妄顧醫護人員和傷者的安危。他又表示急救站貼有十字圖案，救護人員亦穿上容易識別的螢光衣物，警方應該可以區別救護員與示威者，對事件深感遺憾，要求警方徹查交代。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190614/large/1560523117_37f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190614%2Flarge%2F1560523117_37f8.jpg&h=9ba25dad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190614/59717112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59717112&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8Kjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=60124bf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59717112&h=cb173270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190614/59717112</a>"},{"pid":"e0c8ad210940bb06988344c863dbe264f8b5132e","tid":1223787,"uid":141031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T20:03:31.000Z","msg":"要求警方徹查交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務處你哋呢排真係好忙，<br />\n而家個個等你找數啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195c88e8f98c55b55a9eddfe7f247362263850f8","tid":1223787,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T20:06:56.000Z","msg":"出黎開記者會比人屌未呀？<br />\n定係諗住永遠唔交代"}